{"tid":1952973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議員林兆彬: 昨被補人士要除口罩當證物 不過之後不獲發CSI , 只會紙口罩","createTime":"2020-04-01T02:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T05:34:53.000Z","uid":22556,"like":350,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"cd4e603e3bb97fb00b8b1d031b0cae21cb0385a3","tid":1952973,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"【紙口罩？靠害咩！】<br />\n<br />\n我估唔到，凌晨三點，我會喺警署派緊口罩畀喺旺角太子被捕嘅手足&hellip;<br />\n話說今晚有被捕支援律師同我講，原來警方提供畀手足嘅口罩係「紙口罩」😱，而原先手足戴緊嘅口罩會被除下可能當成證物&hellip;<br />\n咁做法今時今日真係可以搞出人命🤬， 點解警方唔向被捕人士提供csi口罩呢？<br />\n希望各位可以關注呢個問題 ，我亦會盡力跟進！💪<br />\n<br />\n#油尖旺區議會防疫包<br />\n#派口罩最有意義係今次<br />\n#旺角警署 #紅磡警署<br />\n<br />\nAlvin Yeung 楊岳橋<br />\nJanet Pang 彭皓昕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/654950198/posts/10157800471370199/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F654950198%2Fposts%2F10157800471370199%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=8c4fbdf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/654950198/posts/10157800471370199/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1d4e9ebcd7785b39bb15066bcc9d13a22f58b958","tid":1952973,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aab4a5e40eddcc58aefb9b7198e2811ab9b6591d","tid":1952973,"uid":68096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9869b396552825ec388f2bf16c6012b8c2b0ca0","tid":1952973,"uid":134087,"like":3,"dislike":353,"score":-350,"citedBy":19,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:12:44.000Z","msg":"公道講, 紙口罩係俗稱，唔係真係紙"},{"pid":"1fd19750e5af692f3ed7333d076a575b8b2749bc","tid":1952973,"uid":44171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"攬炒行動啦"},{"pid":"e8238866782967f6c4048f611293654fb8bc1f91","tid":1952973,"uid":201374,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"e9869b396552825ec388f2bf16c6012b8c2b0ca0","tid":1952973,"uid":1340